Patching UML

@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

' Increase spacing to handle the cables cleanly
skinparam nodesep 100
skinparam ranksep 150

title My bread and butter patching for the Dark Energy II & MS2000BR

component "Korg MS2000BR\n(Virtual Analog / Digital FX)" as Korg {
    portout "Audio Output" as KorgOut
    portout "MIDI Out" as KorgMidi
    portin "Audio Input" as KorgIn
}

component "Doepfer Dark Energy II\n(Analog Semi-Modular)" as DE2 {
    ' Inputs (Top/Left conceptually)
    portin "MIDI In" as DEMidi
    portin "Ext. Audio" as ExtAud
    portin "VCO F (Pitch)" as VCOF
    portin "VCO PW (Width)" as VCOPW
    portin "VCF F (Filter)" as VCFF
    portin "VCA A (Amp)" as VCAA
    
    ' Outputs (Bottom/Right conceptually)
    portout "LFO 1" as LFO1
    portout "Envelope" as Env
    portout "Audio" as AudOut
}

' --- EXISTING PATCHES ---
LFO1 -[#D4AF37,bold]right-> VCFF 
KorgOut -[#E74C3C,bold]down-> ExtAud 
AudOut -[#3498DB,bold]up-> KorgIn 

' --- NEW POTENTIAL PATCHES ---
Env -[#2ECC71,bold]up-> VCOPW 
Env -[#9B59B6,bold]up-> VCOF 
LFO1 -[#E67E22,bold]down-> VCAA 
KorgMidi -[#black,dashed,bold]down-> DEMidi 

legend bottom right
    |= Cable / Color |= Patch Route |= Sonic Result |
    | <color:#D4AF37>■</color> Yellow | LFO 1 ➔ VCF F | **Filter Wobble:** Rhythmic sweeping/pulsing of the filter cutoff. |
    | <color:#E74C3C>■</color> Red | Korg Audio ➔ DE2 Ext. Audio | **Analog Warmth:** Squashes digital polyphony through the analog filter. |
    | <color:#3498DB>■</color> Blue | DE2 Audio ➔ Korg Audio In | **Digital FX:** Processes the raw analog mono signal through Korg effects/vocoder. |
    | <color:#2ECC71>■</color> Green | Envelope ➔ VCO PW | **Phasing Lead:** Modulates pulse width over time for a thick, evolving square wave. |
    | <color:#9B59B6>■</color> Purple | Envelope ➔ VCO F | **Pitch Drop / Percussion:** Creates classic laser sweeps or analog kick drums. |
    | <color:#E67E22>■</color> Orange | LFO 1 ➔ VCA A | **Tremolo / Gate:** Bypasses the filter to chop or rhythmically modulate overall volume. |
    | <color:#000000>■</color> Black (Dashed) | Korg MIDI ➔ DE2 MIDI | **Sequencer Sync:** Triggers the analog synth using the Korg's arpeggiator/sequencer. |
endlegend

@enduml
